(253, 'options_home_middle_text', '&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Tim Dudley is a unique man with a gift for story telling.</h3>\r\n<div class="button hide expand-content">Expand Content</div>\r\n<p class="toggle-text"><img class="alignleft wp-image-103 size-medium" src="http://amannamedtim.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/tim-speaking-sm-300x199.jpg" alt="tim-speaking-sm" width="300" height="199" />His life experiences have been vast and sometimes unconventional. He flunked first grade, and later college, but somehow still managed to overcome failure. He became a gifted teacher, doctor, successful business owner, national rodeo champion, business consultant, and more. He found early on that many conventional means of doing things did not work for him. He will prove to you that making decisions based on GUT is not only important but imperative. Taking ACTION is the key to change and success. Tim''s experiences have proven that when we access GUT, and ACT, we become privileged to occupy a space only the greatest of greats know. It is RARE AIR. The place where inspiration meets hard work. This is the place we all want to be. It''s where great change happens and legends are made. When Tim speaks, people realize how to recognize and make decisions using their GUT and ACT in a way so that they can occupy that sacred space.</p>', 'no'),
