(10537, 'options_testimonial_2_text', 'I''ve had the chance to hear Tim speak on a couple of occasions now, and each time has been captivating and inspiring. A great speaker harnesses the ability to recant personal tales with an angle that can touch the audiences unique interests regardless of subject matter. Tim''s presentation style does just that.', 'no'),
